summary: A young woman who lives in a desert trailer park must choose between caring for her hapless father and sick friend or fulfilling her own destiny.
cast: Agnes Bruckner|Kelli Garner|Justin Long|John Corbett|Gina Gershon|Brian Klugman|Chris Mulkey|Luce Rains|Olive Bureker|Sherry Lynette|Jenny Gabrielle
title: Dreamland
